============================================================
  ARTIFICIAL INTELLIGENCE & MACHINE LEARNING
============================================================

Concept:     Fine-tuning
Category:    Training technique
Definition:  Updates pre-trained model weights on task-specific data
Year:        2018
Researchers: Howard/Ruder (ULMFiT)
Applications:Customizing LLMs, domain adaptation
Related:     Supervised fine-tuning, PEFT, LoRA

Concept:     Transformer
Category:    Architecture
Definition:  Attention-based model processing sequences in parallel
Year:        2017
Researchers: Vaswani et al.
Applications:LLMs, vision models, protein folding
Related:     GPT, BERT, attention mechanism

Concept:     Transfer Learning
Category:    Technique
Definition:  Reuses pre-trained model weights for new related tasks
Year:        2009
Researchers: Pan and Yang survey
Applications:Fine-tuning LLMs, computer vision
Related:     Pre-training, fine-tuning, domain adaptation

============================================================
  DISEASES & MEDICINE
============================================================

Disease:     Tuberculosis
Type:        Bacterial
Pathogen:    M. tuberculosis
Transmission:Airborne droplets
Symptoms:    Persistent cough, night sweats
Treatment:   6-9 month antibiotics
Deaths/yr:   1.6M
Vaccine:     Yes (BCG, partial)
Discovered:  1882

Disease:     Cardiovascular Disease
Type:        Metabolic
Pathogen:    Non-communicable
Transmission:Non-communicable
Symptoms:    Chest pain, shortness of breath
Treatment:   Statins, surgery, stents
Deaths/yr:   17.9M
Vaccine:     No (for most types)
Discovered:  Ancient

Disease:     Cholera
Type:        Bacterial
Pathogen:    Vibrio cholerae
Transmission:Contaminated water
Symptoms:    Profuse watery diarrhea, vomiting
Treatment:   Oral rehydration, antibiotics
Deaths/yr:   0.095M
Vaccine:     Yes
Discovered:  1854

